       000-PROC-SEC                SECTION.
      *
           INITIALIZE                  FLG-AREA
           INITIALIZE                  STS-AREA
           INITIALIZE                  WRK-AREA
      *
           ACCEPT  SYS-TIME            FROM    TIME
      *
      *    各ＤＢ読込
           PERFORM 100-SYORI-SEC
      *
           PERFORM VARYING IDX-SYU     FROM    1   BY  1
                   UNTIL   (IDX-SYU    >   10  )   OR
                           (ORCHCN04-DENPNUM (IDX-SYU) =   ZERO)
               MOVE    ORCHCN04-DENPNUM (IDX-SYU)  TO  WRK-DENPNUM
